gw.api.web.team.summaryrow

Interface TeamSummaryRow

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractTeamSummaryRow, ByActivityTeamSummaryRow, ByRoleTeamSummaryRow, FederatedTeamSummaryRow, InQueueFederatedTeamSummaryRow, InQueueTeamSummaryRow

    public interface TeamSummaryRow
    Facade mapping a TeamSummaryLV row to its data from gw.pc.statistics.entity.UserGroupStats. It thus allows for multiple views on the data in gw.pc.statistics.entity.UserGroupStats. The view type is determined on the supplied StatsType value.

    The current implementations support three views: by-role, by-activity, and the special "In Queue" row.

    See also TeamSummary.pcf.
